column1: Web Site|Meet Loretta|On the Issues|Helping You|Newsroom|Contact MeDear Friend –Sorry to bug you, but there is a really important deadline coming up.
In order to be covered by January 1st under a health insurance plan through Covered California, you must enroll by midnight this Monday, December 15th.
If you're one of the50,000 California that have already enrolled– GREAT!
If you're not, don't wait any longer: visit CoveredCA.com, call (800) 300-1506, orfind in-person local help .
You can also swing by an EnrollOC enrollment event tomorrow at the Santa Ana Bristol Clinic (2720 S. Bristol St.
Santa Ana, CA, 92704) from 8:00 am - 5:00 pm.
If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact my District Office at (714) 621-0102 or visit my website at www.lorettasanchez.house.gov/EnrollOC.
Very truly yours,Loretta SanchezMember of CongressPrivacy Policy|Unsubscribe
